cultivars using PCR-based markers with emphasis on the prevalence of

Al Wijam disease. Arch. Phytopathology and Plant Protection. 2011;
44: 732-42; DOI: 10.1080/03235400802246929
http://www.informaworld.com/smpp/content~db=all~content=a937692589

